{"tid":244253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WannaCry勒索港累計17宗　15個為家庭用戶. 2宗為商用","createTime":"2017-05-15T09:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T10:46:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bc80f905284096e3a845f36c1c16b2bf06b215","tid":244253,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"全球爆發的網絡勒索軟件「WannaCry」(又稱WanaCrypt0r 2.0)肆虐，至今影響150個國家及地區，香港生產力促進局總經理黃永偉表示，今日共收到15宗有關「WannaCry」勒索的舉報，連同上周六及周日各一宗，總數有17宗。他又指，當中15個是家庭用戶，均使用Windows 7作業系統，而另外兩宗則為商用，分別使用Windows Server 2008及Windows 7作業系統。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170515/mobile/bkn-20170515171547611-0515_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170515%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170515171547611-0515_00822_001.html&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f8f9bbae\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170515/mobile/bkn-20170515171547611-0515_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca275e280492b7b3067b48b60c37a8769b817566","tid":244253,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"355257e0199ec8b97cfdee306f34b6942920b853","tid":244253,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21d457bab84ddb3e114788262203d2d1e4603554","tid":244253,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"原來咁撚少"},{"pid":"239de795c599d07b11677df7a2620c9ba16c180c","tid":244253,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來咁撚少</blockquote><br />\n網上行同hkbn晨早就block左port先爆大獲"},{"pid":"97759b4a4efc4f24e3997d73184af92ddd2091c7","tid":244253,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來咁撚少</blockquote><br />\n網上行同hkbn晨早就